s, smoked salmon and cherry tomatoes into baking dish. Season with salt and pepper, then set baking dish aside."},{"content":"Place onion and leek into mixing bowl and chop <b>5 sec\/speed 6<b>."},{"content":"Add bacon and chop <b>2-4 sec\/speed 4<b>, until evenly chopped. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula."},{"content":"Add olive oil and sauté <b>5 min\/120°C\/speed 1<b>. Spread onion, leek and bacon mixture over fish and salmon in baking dish, then set baking dish aside. Clean and dry mixing bowl."},{"isHeader":true,"content":"Velouté sauce"},{"content":"Place parsley into mixing bowl and chop <b>3 sec\/speed 7<b>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula."},{"content":"Add all remaining sauce ingredients and cook <b>5 min\/90°C\/speed 4<b>. Transfer sauce into baking dish over onion and bacon mixture. Set baking dish aside in the refrigerator. Clean and dry mixing bowl."},{"isHeader":true,"content":"Mashed potato"},{"content":"Place Parmesan into mixing bowl and grate <b>10 sec\/speed 9<b>. Transfer into a bowl and set aside. Rinse and dry mixing bowl."},{"content":" <strong>Insert butterfly whisk.<\/strong> Place potatoes, salt and milk into mixing bowl and cook <b>25 min\/95°C\/speed 1<b>, placing simmering basket instead of measuring cup onto mixing bowl lid."},{"content":"Add butter, nutmeg (optional) and reserved grated Parmesan, <strong>insert measuring cup<\/strong> and mash <b>30 sec\/speed 3<b>."},{"content":"Transfer mashed potato into baking dish and spread over evenly using spatula. Scatter extra butter shavings on top and bake for 40 minutes (180°C). Leave to stand for 5 minutes in baking dish before serving."}],"hintsAndTricks":["Please refer to <i>The Basic Cookbook<\/i> for the Vegetable stock paste recipe."],"basicInfo":["easy","30m","2h","6 portions"]}